race.description: Pelican Rocks Cafe Country Boosted Mdn Plate
race.comment: TREASURE HUNTER (3) prepared well and then led well-supported here on debut, narrowly beaten. Draws inside and Collett sticking aboard is a plus. Fitter and will be tougher to peg back. DANCING MAN (1) didn't have the best of it here last time, but was heading in the right direction prior. Maps low today and has a 3kg claimer booked. Hard fit now and deserves another chance. GODDESS MINERVA (4) was beaten less than 2L in the TREASURE HUNTER race. Will be fitter again and has claims. HIS AIN'T TEXAS (8) and DANCING MUMMA (7) both debut for smart yards and are likely to race well. The betting will be key with them.
